reviewText: Grandchildren said we had to have these
Was here in good time, only thing was the case was broke on the bottom and it's a double disk case so I can't just get a new one very easily.

Wonderful movies with an adult twist on them!  Every grown up out there should see these. So very entertaining. Quick delivery and great price.
Terry W
Grove City, Ohio
Both of these movies are worth watching, even more than once.
